          <h1 id="Creating components">Creating components</h1>
          
          <div class="va-introtext" markdown="1">
            A guide to creating components in Figma at VA. Following this guide ensures that any component you contribute will meet the quality standards set by the Design System.
          </div>
          
          
            
<nav aria-labelledby="on-this-page" class="site-on-this-page">
  <dl class="site-on-this-page__list">
